:: Darkangel ::

He turned from the window to face Tyrael.

Darkangel: No I havn't taken a beast mode yet. I have an idea for one 
though. I think a bat would suit me. Especially a Vampire bat. I 
should go take care of that.

Darkangel starts to head off but turns to the window one last time.

Darkangel: It is a beautifull planet. To be yet more beautifull under 
the Tripredacus flag.

Darkangel continues on to the scanning room, to take his beast mode.
